Compact IF Statement
--------------------

Normal code     ->1
-----------
number = 10

if number > 0:
    print('Positive')


Compact code     ->1
------------
number = 10

if number > 0: print('Positive')


Ternary operator
----------------

Normal code  ->2
-----------
grade = 40

if grade >= 50:
    result = 'pass'
else:
    result = 'fail'

print(result)


compact code    ->2
------------
grade = 40

result = 'pass' if number >= 50 else 'fail'

print(result)